# WakaTime / Hackatime local artifacts.
# These normally live in your HOME dir (~/.wakatime.cfg, ~/.wakatime/), NOT here —
# listed defensively so a stray project-local copy is never committed.
# (*.log above already covers .wakatime.log.) The .wakatime-project file is
# intentionally NOT ignored: it pins the project name and SHOULD be committed.
.wakatime.cfg
.wakatime.db
.wakatime.bdb
.wakatime-internal.cfg
.wakatime/

